member.summary:
   Looks up a localized string similar to Selection of ready-to-use preset from a drop-down list.
The list contains:
- named user's sets you had saved;
- application-predefined default set(s), if any;
- up to 9 last used sets (history)

Text box uses for entering a name for a new user preset..

members.member:
Reads GIF image from stream

@param BufferedInputStream containing GIF file.
@return read status code (0 = no errors)

Reads color table as 256 RGB integer values

@param ncolors int number of colors to read
@return int array containing 256 colors (packed ARGB with full alpha)

Gets the "Netscape" iteration count, if any.
A count of 0 means repeat indefinitiely.

@return iteration count if one was specified, else 1.
